      "id": "PopularPost312061",
      "post_content": "@StayFrostyK: You're not thinking of different formats. Obviously for Constructed you'd use the Keyrunes or Chromatic Lantern, but for Dragon's Maze Limited these are essential for the mana fixing there; any higher rarity and it wouldn't work. So of course there's not going to be powerful compared to competition in different rarities and intended for entirely different formats. Unless you want [Chromatic Lantern](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chromatic Lantern) at common?  \n  \nAnd we want them to draw *two* cards? That's too much draw for colours that shouldn't have it, like Boros or Gruul colours. The single draw replaces them so they replace themselves when their function is done, and that's all it needs.  \n  ",
      "posted_by": "Splizer",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost312061\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">@StayFrostyK: You're not thinking of different formats. Obviously for Constructed you'd use the Keyrunes or Chromatic Lantern, but for Dragon's Maze Limited these are essential for the mana fixing there; any higher rarity and it wouldn't work. So of course there's not going to be powerful compared to competition in different rarities and intended for entirely different formats. Unless you want <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chromatic Lantern\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chromatic Lantern\">Chromatic Lantern</a> at common?<br/><br/>And we want them to draw <i>two</i> cards? That's too much draw for colours that shouldn't have it, like Boros or Gruul colours. The single draw replaces them so they replace themselves when their function is done, and that's all it needs.<br/><br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '312061'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy60734\">Splizer</span>\r\n                                (4/25/2013 3:16:57 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </d