    {
      "id": "PopularPost311580",
      "post_content": "Clue stones are awful. Can't stand them. With things like [darksteel ingot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=darksteel ingot) and [chromatic lantern](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=chromatic lantern) for 3, who would want to limit themselves with only 2 colors for still 3 mana? And the card draw ability should be 2 colorless instead of one of each of the assigned guilds colors to make it good at all. For one of each mana in that guild AND sacrificing this mana producing artifact we should be allowed to draw TWO cards, not one.",
      "posted_by": "StayFrostyK",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost311580\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Clue stones are awful. Can't stand them. With things like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"darksteel ingot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=darksteel ingot\">darksteel ingot</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"chromatic lantern\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=chromatic lantern\">chromatic lantern</a> for 3, who would want to limit themselves with only 2 colors for still 3 mana? And the card draw ability should be 2 colorless instead of one of each of the assigned guilds colors to make it good at all. For one of each mana in that guild AND sacrificing this mana producing artifact we should be allowed to draw TWO cards, not one.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '311580'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy96314\">StayFrostyK</span>\r\n                                (4/24/2013 5:11:15 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_p